{"tid":2210251,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得今年真係好孤獨","createTime":"2020-09-20T09:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T11:58:20.000Z","uid":71302,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d87214e1b3a25c5dd9cab589d29b9e2404688725","tid":2210251,"uid":71302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"我仲讀緊書既<br />\n今年上半年真係主要stay係屋企<br />\n始終學校咩都cancel曬<br />\n每日就係stay屋企 開zoom熄zoom<br />\n無錯係多左好多時間打機同睇戲<br />\n但唔出街唔見fd 個人覺得好孤獨<br />\n好多朋友自動無左contact<br />\n因為以前見面都係話要約食飯或者去玩<br />\n4-6月出返街 7-8月又完全係屋企<br />\n到9月仲zoom緊 好似無得回復正常<br />\n咁樣既環境下 好似真係會無曬d朋友<br />\n無曬所有活動 覺得今年真係好孤單<br />\n就算回復正常 都返唔到去以前咁<br />\n仲要唔知幾時先可以回復正常<br />\n出面班連登毒撚仲歌頌又可以zoom<br />\n但係個代價係人際關係疏離又無得旅行<br />\n點解仲會覺得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a90f799de99d233e52961fc71ba084ee2534914","tid":2210251,"uid":263618,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9decca983cd45c4c9b48e377bac3b5160421562","tid":2210251,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:24:55.000Z","msg":"孤獨是好事"},{"pid":"4e6e9013aca0887d5a295ea3f449aa7d53667179","tid":2210251,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />非常覺，唔知可以點"},{"pid":"1175884eea6053c06fdea276ea63df0f0c3f6d36","tid":2210251,"uid":118709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"其實毒撚一個更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f196a12f52e4be7df83654db7dfd964b3f18c56","tid":2210251,"uid":323977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:30:18.000Z","msg":"全部都酒肉朋友 可有可無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a94d80997fa56af068f22d51846e5336d5fe82f","tid":2210251,"uid":45977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1